# Tracked-but-empty marker so the `logs/` directory exists in fresh checkouts.
#
# `scripts/mainnet-deploy.sh` writes deploy logs to
# `logs/mainnet-deploy-<UTC-ISO8601>.log`. The log files themselves are
# excluded by the repo-root `*.log` rule in `.gitignore`; rotation to
# long-term storage is operator-driven and out of scope for this repo.
#
# See ADR-080 §5.
